~ This is a special news bulliten ~ 
We have just been informed that a neighboring town has been over run, and in immediate
need of assistance.  We need your help!

Draw a random town tile and place it on the edge of the city, your goal(s) now includes 
eliminating all enemies that are entrenched in that town.  All enemies gain a +2 to their
hit points and hit.  Place two enemies on each area in the new map.
All players also gain two Stimulants and one Condomnation cards.  If an Event card is 
drawn, that must be played immediately and all events on that card must be followed along
with this card
